<li id="cite_note-NWC219-10">^ <a href="#cite_ref-NWC219_10-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-NWC219_10-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-NWC219_10-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-NWC219_10-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-NWC219_10-4" title=""><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#CITEREFProctor1999" title="">Proctor 1999</a>, p.&#160;219</li>
<li id="cite_note-BMJGDS-11">^ <a href="#cite_ref-BMJGDS_11-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BMJGDS_11-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BMJGDS_11-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-BMJGDS_11-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFGeorge_Davey_Smith2004">George Davey Smith (December 2004), "<a href="http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/329/7480/1424" class="external text" title="http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/329/7480/1424" rel="nofollow">Lifestyle, health, and health promotion in Nazi Germany</a>", <i>British Medical Journal</i> <b>329</b> (7480): 1424–5, <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fbmj.329.7480.1424" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1136%2Fbmj.329.7480.1424" rel="nofollow">10.1136/bmj.329.7480.1424</a></span>, <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15604167" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15604167">PMID 15604167</a>, <a href="/wiki/PubMed_Central" title="PubMed Central">PMC</a>: <a href="http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pmcentrez&amp;artid=535959" class="external text" title="http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pmcentrez&amp;artid=535959" rel="nofollow">535959</a><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/329/7480/1424" class="external free" title="http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/329/7480/1424" rel="nofollow">http://www.bmj.com/cgi/content/full/329/7480/1424</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved on 2008-07-01</span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Lifestyle%2C+health%2C+and+health+promotion+in+Nazi+Germany&amp;rft.jtitle=British+Medical+Journal&amp;rft